  "description": "<i>K?shien 4</i> is a baseball goal that allows players to compete in a Japanese high school league. The game has more modes and features compared not only to its immediate <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/kshien-3\">predecessor</a>, but also the first two games. Team creation mode is back, this time offering more advanced customization options. It is possible to customize names, numbers, uniforms, and faces of the players (including detailed options for facial features). Practice mode has been expanded as well, allowing training of separate players. Core gameplay mechanics remain the same as in the previous installments. Visually, the game distinguishes itself from its predecessors by feature &quot;super-deformed&quot; character graphics with a slight comical angle.",
